| Context: To grill the salmon fillets, first preheat the grill to medium-high heat. Next, brush the fish with olive oil and season with lemon pepper. Then, place the fillets skin-side down on the grates. After that, cook for six minutes without flipping. Finally, turn the fish over and grill for another four minutes until flaky. | Input: {"question": "List the actions in order."} | Output: {"answer": ["preheat the grill to medium-high heat", "brush the fish with olive oil and season with lemon pepper", "place the fillets skin-side down on the grates", "cook for six minutes without flipping", "turn the fish over and grill for another four minutes until flaky"]}

