| Context: To replace a light bulb, begin by switching off the power at the circuit breaker. Allow the old bulb to cool down if it was recently on. Grip the glass gently and twist counter-clockwise to remove it from the socket. Insert the new bulb and twist clockwise until it is snug. Restore power at the breaker and test the switch to ensure it works. | Input: {"question": "What steps were taken?"} | Output: {"answer": ["switching off the power at the circuit breaker", "Allow the old bulb to cool down if it was recently on", "Grip the glass gently and twist counter-clockwise to remove it from the socket", "Insert the new bulb and twist clockwise until it is snug", "Restore power at the breaker and test the switch to ensure it works"]}

| Context: The tea making ritual begins by boiling fresh water in a kettle. Warm the teapot by swirling a little hot water inside and discarding it. Place two tea bags into the pot and pour the boiling water over them. Let the tea steep for exactly five minutes to develop flavor. Pour the brewed tea into cups and serve with honey or lemon slices. | Input: {"question": "List the actions in order."} | Output: {"answer": ["boiling fresh water in a kettle", "Warm the teapot by swirling a little hot water inside and discarding it", "Place two tea bags into the pot and pour the boiling water over them", "Let the tea steep for exactly five minutes to develop flavor", "Pour the brewed tea into cups and serve with honey or lemon slices"]}

